## 3. Animation Specifications

| Animation | Duration | Easing | Properties | Stagger |
|-----------|----------|--------|------------|---------|
| Theme transition | 0.25s | ease | background-color, border-color, color | — |
| KPI entrance | 0.2s | easeOut | opacity 0→1, y 10→0 | index × 0.05s |
| KPI count-up | 0.6s | easeOut | numeric value 0→final | — |
| Widget hover | 0.2s | ease | scale 1→1.02, shadow | — |
| Widget click | 0.2s | ease | scale 0.98 | — |
| Widget entrance | 0.2s | easeOut | opacity 0→1 | index × 0.05s |
| Modal content | 0.25s | easeOut | opacity 0→1, scale 0.95→1 | — |
| Table rows | 0.15s | ease | opacity 0→1 | rowIndex × 0.03s |

